transcript:
The Queen:
[Beth is a captive]
This was wandering about. 
[shoves Beth]

The Queen:
Do something original with her! 
[goes on her way]

D'Arcy:
[behind Queen's back]
Gargoyle! 
The Queen:
[looks back]
Beg your pardon? 
D'Arcy:
[back in toady mode]
Superb, you're superb! 
The Queen:
Good boy! | This was wandering about Do something original with her Gargoyle Beg your pardon Superb you're superb Good boy

movie_title: The Perils of Gwendoline in the Land of the Yik Yak
movie_writer: Just Jaeckin, John Willie, Jean-Luc Voulfow
movie_plot: Gwendoline, a runaway nun, arrives in Hong Kong on a mission to find her father, who was last seen in the legendary Land of the Yik Yak searching for a rare butterfly. She's guided on her perilous journey by the selfish mercenary Wil
